content: How many tables can I have in my log?
You can have up to 100 tables in a log.
What the maximum number of data files I can load?
The maximum number of data files you can load is unlimited.
How many curves can I load in one go?
You can load up to 450 curves at a time.
How many symbols can I have in the plot at any one time?
You can have up to 10,000 symbols in a plot at any given time.
